channel.title: Azeroth Online Project (In Need of Coders)
channel.description:
[b]Here is some basic Information on the project at hand.[/b]
[u]Project Name: Azeroth Online Project source base: Unknown. definitely a 508[sup]RSHDPS[/sup] Team: Matrix Incorporates[/u]
I need more coders to begin the project. We will not be starting anytime soon due to the switch off of wL but i'd like to just get everything set up.[sup]if it takes too long we'll start then worry about it later.[/sup]
What im looking for is an Economy Based server, it'll be a 508, hard cash, hard leveling, and hard items. Almost NO commands. We'll get into more detail when the team is brought together but as of now. Just please PM me, E-Mail me([sub]matrixincorporated@ymail.com[/sub]), or contact me through my site. http://www.matrixincorporated.
Main language will be in Java programming as most users know it best.
A test will be created and this board will be updated. as of now PM me then when it is created everyone will take the test
